bas-ui (1.0.1) testing; urgency=medium

  * Refactor image loading: add wx/images module with imageLoadAsset, imageLoadFile,
    renderSvgToWxImage (nanosvg); ImageSet delegates to it, BitmapMode.include_raw.
  * UI frame/fragment lifecycle: uiFrame uses addFragment() + createView();
    UIFragment createFragmentView/destroyFragmentView, elements().
  * Centralize ID allocation: BuildViewContext.getNextId(); UIStateValueDescriptor
    id(context) for menu/tool IDs; resolveGroup/addToTree take BuildViewContext*.
  * ENUM state: toolbar tools use descriptor icons; findValueById for event handling.

 -- Lenik (谢继雷) <lenik@bodz.net>  Wed, 18 Mar 2026 00:00:00 +0000

